  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, FUNDI seeks to link the unemployed/underemployed in South Africa with job opportunities. For those who gather at approximately 1,000 informal sites across the country each day in hopes of finding casual labor jobs so that they can provide for themselves and their families, FUNDI provides a reliable system that enables them to obtain greater levels of employment and know their rights as workers.</narrative>
